{"tid":1626934,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔係好同意而家講緊的舖頭四大分類","createTime":"2019-10-05T13:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:55:48.000Z","uid":254452,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"806d7a57658052e435e012680022b2284e134b4f","tid":1626934,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:43:10.000Z","msg":"當然,各位手足會重新審視行動的細節,作檢討係一件好事。<br />\n我見隔離POST有成6千幾正評的新分類,但我唔係幾同意,想講出黎比大家諗下。<br />\n<br />\n本身<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span></span>分類簡單易記 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">紅裝修,藍罷買,黃懲罰</span>唔應該改左佢。<br />\n<br />\n而且,我見大家講改的例子,其實好唔合理。<br />\n先唔講一般中資,<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三中商</span></span>係屬於中聯辦,好明顯就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共的文宣機器之一</span></span>,但大家討論竟然都只係跌左落紅,而唔入黑。雖然呢場運動入面三中商無直接做過咩事害手足,但不嬲都話,只要係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屬於共黨BOSS的手手腳腳,一律都要不停扣佢血,我地先有得贏。</span></span><br />\n而且唔好唔記得,三中商近年都不停篡改教科書內容,洗下一代的腦,如果佢地都只係紅的話,我覺得大家個思維仲係太單純,我地的贏面會細左好多!唔該大家清醒少少,諗清楚!唔好比人帶走左!<br />\n<br />\n至於見大家又討論話美心都跌落<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span></span>而唔係去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑</span></span>,大佬呀,個太子女咁神心上埋去聯合國發言,撐黑警,屌示威者,又要打壓罷課學生,做咁多陰質野,都只係紅? 你地訓醒未呀?<br />\n<br />\n我個人意見,維持<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span></span>分類不變。<br />\n同時,分類準則係所有港共,政府,黑社會,以及出過手做實際野打壓示威者,害手足的,都會係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span></span>!例如<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">優品360,美心,福建麻雀館</span></span><br />\n而只係口頭上撐警、屌示威者的,就繼續係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span></span>店,我地罷買罷食,唔裝修,例如<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">養心殿,陳根記</span></span><br />\n黃店唔洗講啦,一定大大力懲罰<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span></span>!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span></span>!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span></span>!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span></span>!"},{"pid":"52b6988a29af1ab89fa19ab8e2901c94d88022c8","tid":1626934,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"請支持行動post<br />\n<br />\n【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"191977b57ea90b577ba9f48473d1324f6419a196","tid":1626934,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:55:15.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"21a354e94cacab7e8cd31fd10c0c4d845c0f3332","tid":1626934,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"美國夠有支共媒體 set up <br />\n代唔代表 FBI CIA homeland security 要幫佢裝修？"},{"pid":"2bf0ec2c6fcca1dcc1fd28c7f4bef7288e1bb0bc","tid":1626934,"uid":254452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21a354e94cacab7e8cd31fd10c0c4d845c0f3332","tid":1626934,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"美國夠有支共媒體 set up <br />\n代唔代表 FBI CIA homeland security 要幫佢裝修？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5687e7b0f21350d5d1b4e653cb7d559806600083","tid":1626934,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:04:01.000Z","msg":"多謝你意見<br />\n不過唔同意"},{"pid":"683baff1cea9e336c15579c296ba262f33bd8669","tid":1626934,"uid":30868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:09:02.000Z","msg":"裝修係絕招黎, 你要定好個目標, 唔能夠個個壞人都去搞<br />\n我地個目標係裝修D最仆街既商戶, 令到其他商戶改變行為唔做仆街野<br />\n要裝修最嚴重果D, 其他果D我地成功先再清算<br />\n我地而家係要呢D友仔獨善其身先"},{"pid":"aa2f611f79e0c46daba091cef030a3110e34d33c","tid":1626934,"uid":254452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"683baff1cea9e336c15579c296ba262f33bd8669","tid":1626934,"uid":30868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:09:02.000Z","msg":"裝修係絕招黎, 你要定好個目標, 唔能夠個個壞人都去搞<br />\n我地個目標係裝修D最仆街既商戶, 令到其他商戶改變行為唔做仆街野<br />\n要裝修最嚴重果D, 其他果D我地成功先再清算<br />\n我地而家係要呢D友仔獨善其身先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"咁講既話,商店方面即係剩番優品360、麻雀館要裝修?<br />\n佢地出埋刀手無疑係最仆街,但文鬥方面美心上到去聯合國咁高端,即係想煮死我地,三中商唔係普通中資,直情係中聯辦黎,都唔係最高級別?<br />\n